{"tid":1052200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"精壯男想約砲再一發　竟用性愛片恐嚇正妹玩4P","createTime":"2019-03-08T06:39:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T02:34:13.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3523efc7958a35f12276490a57641fc99f708bad","tid":1052200,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T06:39:24.000Z","msg":"身材精壯的男子湯程家去年8月在交友軟體Tinder認識一名女子，並相約見面後，女子事後控告湯男涉嫌在兩人嘿咻時偷拍性愛片，藉此威脅她「再來一次」，甚至想玩4P，女子因此怒告湯男恐嚇等罪，湯男起初否認犯案，事後才承認用性愛片威脅女子，並賠償女子約10萬元達成和解，台北地檢署今以恐嚇罪給予湯男緩起訴2年，並要求湯男寫悔過書並上10小時法治教育課程。<br />\n湯男去年曾向《蘋果》喊冤稱，是女子同意他才拍攝性愛影片，但並未揚言要散布女子影片或對女子不利，可能是因為女子事後要求刪除影片時，他順勢詢問想二度約會，讓女子感受不佳，他十分抱歉。<br />\n但檢警調查，去年8月13日湯男和女子相約在租屋處見面後，兩人發生性關係並拍攝性愛影片，但事後女子認為不妥要求湯男刪除，湯男卻沒照做，甚至還想約女子再度嘿咻，女子不肯，湯男就傳送性愛影片的截圖給女子，還傳訊「有看到嗎？臉」、「我有個提議，你跟我和朋友玩，3男」、「不要搞鬼，否則我朋友會上傳影片」等語，女子嚇得趕緊報案，並假裝同意見面，釣出湯男逮人。<br />\n檢警搜索湯男住處時，果真找到被害女子的性愛影片，但離譜的是，湯男還蒐藏了自己和其他女子的性愛影片，但由於妨害秘密罪屬告訴乃論罪，因未有其他受害人報案，湯男也否認偷拍，因此其他女子性愛影片部分無法究責。<br />\n而湯男應訊時起初否認恐嚇女子，事後才坦承利用性愛影片要求女子再度赴約，雙方經調解後，湯男承諾賠償女子約10萬元，女子也願意原諒湯男，並撤回妨害秘密罪告訴，但因恐嚇罪屬於公訴罪，北檢考量雙方和解，湯男也認罪，因此給予湯男緩起訴2年、但須寫悔過書並上10小時法治教育課程。（吳珮如／台北報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190308/640_b9ff6906bca356c738f40f9665daeb74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190308%2F640_b9ff6906bca356c738f40f9665daeb74.jpg&h=996c6571&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n湯程家曾現身喊冤，事後卻認罪賠償受害人獲緩起訴。<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20190308/1529593/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20190308%2F1529593%2F&d=fEJCtfATBeMWJ6YDVJZPMswxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=97bbe63a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20190308%2F1529593%2F&h=b38c542b\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20190308/1529593/</a>"},{"pid":"d4a6a7e803d8ea14e0481c6e3d9625f16839aab5","tid":1052200,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T06:42:25.000Z","msg":"仲以為唔係台灣, 係香港添 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fca18c078cee7c5996de990fb6f172661180235","tid":1052200,"uid":135840,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T06:43:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xPGajaO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxPGajaO.png&h=505ee05c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea81722c5974bc0861e35527426e0faedf24edc7","tid":1052200,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6fca18c078cee7c5996de990fb6f172661180235","tid":1052200,"uid":135840,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T06:43:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xPGajaO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxPGajaO.png&h=505ee05c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T06:44:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c25e4c1e801113dbd73ecfcaf8b0c80037c43ffd","tid":1052200,"uid":156376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T06:44:38.000Z","msg":"咁撚似毒坤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b57eb5e0483583288262aa877fb8af8d4ba0be51","tid":1052200,"uid":7741,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T06:45:17.000Z","msg":"幾靚仔咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a2e15cac7a64a293c0effd401cfe57a2a1823a","tid":1052200,"uid":122217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6fca18c078cee7c5996de990fb6f172661180235","tid":1052200,"uid":135840,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T06:43:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xPGajaO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxPGajaO.png&h=505ee05c&s={S